title: 07: WWDC 2016 aftermath
description: WWDC 2016 has come and gone, and Gartenberg, Caldwell, and Ritchie break it all down. From watchOS 3 to tvOS 10, macOS Sierra to iOS 10, here's what it all means… and portends.
